text: Colobothea signatipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lameere in 1884. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Colobothea signatipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1884
title: Colobothea signatipennis
